gobblin.metrics.context

Interface ReportableContext

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    InnerMetricContext, MetricContext, RootMetricContext

    public interface ReportableContext
    Interface for a context that can be reported (e.g. InnerMetricContext, MetricContext).
